p: Subpoena Territory of Washington County of Lincoln}ss To W. Foreman In the name of the United States, You are hereby required to appear before the undersigned, one of the Justices of the Peace and for said County, on the forthwith day of 188 o'clock M, at his office in Sprague W.T. to give evidence in a certain cause then and there to be tried between Territory of Washington Plaintiff and E. Romick Defendant, on the part of the Defendant Given under my hand this 27th day of February 1885 E. Pendleton Justice of the Peace
